summary:
An enthusiastic and conscientious
social worker / coordinator with
over eight years of experience in
the healthcare and social sector, in particular
in providing professional care to
children, the elderly, refugees,
orphans, sick and disabled
patients. Three years of
coordination experience in elderly
sector. One year of social
experience sector and deal directly
with women and children fleeing
domestic violence. Three years of
experience as a social worker of
humanitarian missions in Africa an
medical mission with refugees from
Syria and Iraq. Motivated and
driven to provide the best possible
support to customers who need
help, support and social care.
